IN MY OPINION THE CORONAVIRUS CAN BE STOPPED IN 1 MONTH IF:
1. All flights in The United States should be suspended for 2 weeks. (in planes everyone can become infected faster or people can bring virus from one state to another.
2. All people in The United States should buy enough food for 2 weeks and all should stay home for 2 weeks. Also everything should be closed.
3. Those that are sick in this 2 week period should go straight to the hospital.
4. All states in the USA should close its borders for 2 weeks. ( no one can get in, no one can get out )
5. Law enforcement should monitor any illegal activity (like people being outside ) in their own counties and cities.
6. Everyone should live more a healthy lifestyle in this period. For cold, flu and some viruses is good to drink a small shot of lemon juice, garlic, ginger, and honey. (check with your doctor ) also stay hydrated and eat chicken soup which is also good for cold and flu season.

snippet.textDisplay: The entire world cannot wait for a vaccine to be made before going back to “normal” life. Some economies around the world can barely survive when the population is working and consuming. If we don’t get the people back out there spending money and working, then things will get much worse. I think it’s going to get to a point where you will be required by law to wear a face mask and rubber gloves in order to be out in the public. We will never get to zero cases in the next few years, so there will always be a risk of the virus spreading again. We need a short term solution that limits the amount of deaths and doesn’t require everyone to put their life on pause, while scientists develop a vaccine. Staying inside is not the short term answer to save us. It’s just a reaction to slow down the inevitable.
